{"tid":872953,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"聖鬥士星矢外傳《聖鬥少女翔》動畫12月聖誕開播","createTime":"2018-10-23T05:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T10:13:20.000Z","uid":51665,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6fcbdb76dc077b33a6febc91e7dd193139e67b6e","tid":872953,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"聖鬥士星矢外傳《聖鬥少女翔》動畫12月聖誕開播\t<br />\n燃燒吧小宇宙~~熱血的記憶雅典娜的聖鬥士又返來啦&hellip;.而且仲係處少女翔呀&hellip;.呀.. 呀&hellip;呀..<br />\n<br />\n聖鬥士星矢原來係唔會被時代淘汰，原作者車田正美嘅另一套《聖鬥士星矢》外傳作品《聖鬥少女翔》已經推出動畫，滿足並勾起大家對《聖鬥士星矢》嘅愛！而且主角仲係女呀<br />\n<br />\n本作的時間線，在翔子成為聖鬥少女之前是原作中的「銀河戰爭篇」期間，成為了聖鬥處少女之後是在「十二宮篇」之後。咁即佢地可能有機會見到星矢佢地，幻想一下如果比小馬座的翔子遇見天馬座的星矢，到底翔子同雅典娜呢兩個女人的關系會有咩野轉變？(要等TVB拍出來睇睇！)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=318917\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D318917&h=179f23ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這套外傳由久織ちまき負責畫，其實早於於兩年前宣布動畫化，當時我地menclub都有報導，今年12月終於確定在Animax on Playstation上播出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=318920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D318920&h=cde86187&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《聖鬥少女翔》係描述守護女神雅典娜嘅「聖鬥少女」嘅故事，而翔就係其中一位聖鬥少女小馬座，亦係故事嘅女主角。車田正美有提過，自己一直有關於貼身保護雅典娜嘅聖鬥士少女隊Idea，亦希望可以將同男性不同嘅少女纖細面表現出嚟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=318925\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D318925&h=fa3691b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原作中的黃金聖鬥士 - 天蠍座米羅及獅子座 尼奧亦會登場，天蠍座更是令主角翔子成為聖鬥少女之路的重要推助力。<br />\n<br />\n是次聲優是由下面陣容負責眾少女們，原聲CD大碟也會在12月展推出，唔知主題曲可否好像之前舊聖鬥士星矢主題曲咁Hit吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=318916\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D318916&h=af23448b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M2utLODX38g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM2utLODX38g&d=sQ4YyRmqG3u9s5iFVk398CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=39417371\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M2utLODX38g</a><br />\n聲優鈴木愛奈主演翔子<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/api.php?mod=objects.show&amp;object_id=318921\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fapi.php%3Fmod%3Dobjects.show%26object_id%3D318921&h=755406e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《聖鬥士星矢 聖鬥少女翔》將於今年12月24日本播出。<br />\n依家d女性鬥士唔戴面具又坦胸露膊咁淫賤真係西風日下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7ad5d7ede143a6bbf0c86f3b0b7357a57bc770","tid":872953,"uid":9091,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"On9冇面具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廿年星矢迷"},{"pid":"c2f85754fbaf089d29e2f5a2c9c5e64258a50f49","tid":872953,"uid":18241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"性鬥士黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d01540d043d9b40c774056ce2aab979323884484","tid":872953,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"希望天蠍座係關俊彥配返，近排唔多見佢老人家"},{"pid":"01b2251f78d58e037811163f202dead196bfd56e","tid":872953,"uid":35773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:31:42.000Z","msg":"主角應該有丁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係就要帶面具"},{"pid":"9328ada9cccd64869f6fd28ca1340f47bb94fa6e","tid":872953,"uid":143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:32:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e370a5c43719a9dfe5f71ea47bbf298f501be69","tid":872953,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"小馬座，可以騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmo